{"tid":1618345,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東網：消息指政府已決定引用緊急法為禁蒙面立法","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:49:04.000Z","uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9abf97029ba26708006ac8531612b4450cb4a3","tid":1618345,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"link後補"},{"pid":"2748a35c476e01a990642b7ea7c8c29f7838703d","tid":1618345,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191004/bkn-20191004091636815-1004_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191004%2Fbkn-20191004091636815-1004_00822_001.html&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3vCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=2d3ebd84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191004/bkn-20191004091636815-1004_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ddf959ab705e0d5e59bd92334caabc1c89cdb59","tid":1618345,"uid":137041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"屌佢老尾"},{"pid":"7a7be1482f0e29c56f0e5f99ef521edaf7caf952","tid":1618345,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"香港過去近4個月捲入修訂《逃犯條例》衝突旋渦，且示威者暴力程度不斷升級。有消息指，港府對《禁蒙面法》研究已進入最後階段，行政會議今早(4日)召開特別會議，決定引用《緊急情況規例條例》(簡稱《緊急法》)為禁蒙面立法。<br />\n<br />\n行會成員葉劉淑儀、張國鈞、任志剛、羅范椒芬等人早上約9時抵達特首辦。有指政府認為《禁蒙面法》可賦予警方更大權力，應付違法示威，但不擔心會影響人身自由，若任由情況惡化反而保障不到市民的自由。<br />\n<br />\n《禁蒙面法》主要針對市民參與政治活動時不准蒙面，特別是非法集會及遊行，但有合理辯解除外。此外，由於警方目前最多可拘留被捕人士48小時，惟近日拘捕大量人士，人手未及處理，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府亦正研究引用《緊急法》延長拘留時間。</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e7f51aa9bdb9234d8b4d10c74be9599c2315334","tid":1618345,"uid":160102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"帶頭破壞法治"},{"pid":"9bc367b9acb9ed07a2095d9a61c37373b9c2722d","tid":1618345,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪就係獨栽囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2868d0874b8da1485bce27e13b19feb343d08089","tid":1618345,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"真係on9無極限"},{"pid":"85c24ce1d7312c9c90f0299a16288774a3db8397","tid":1618345,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4d099431f07a4fa89dd4b02d3ede3019179706","tid":1618345,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"法治社會，笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b5f4df9e59ba1559c48bfc1c8b773699f4bf43","tid":1618345,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"大律師公會 同所有正常既律師<br />\n可唔可以早佢一步用司法覆核或其他手段<br />\n先阻止佢地用緊急法<br />\n<br />\n或者美國出聲<br />\n一用緊急法立即終止香港所有特別待遇？"},{"pid":"792f8a0fd5b4e0e591631c3b2c26acace016d183","tid":1618345,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b5f4df9e59ba1559c48bfc1c8b773699f4bf43","tid":1618345,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"大律師公會 同所有正常既律師<br />\n可唔可以早佢一步用司法覆核或其他手段<br />\n先阻止佢地用緊急法<br />\n<br />\n或者美國出聲<br />\n一用緊急法立即終止香港所有特別待遇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:49:04.000Z","msg":"Solomon Yue lobby緊制裁林鄭同行會成員"}]}